query:
SELECT 
  u.id, u.email, 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM userEducation WHERE userId = u.id) as educationCount,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM userEmployment WHERE userId = u.id) as employmentCount
FROM users u 
WHERE u.role='trainee' 
ORDER BY u.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 5;
